# Beta stats queries

When the user asks for **beta stats**, **city demand**, **Go activity**, or similar, run these against Supabase project `dmgxrcmdihgsffvqllms` via MCP `execute_sql` (or `apply_migration` only for DDL). Present results clearly; default window is last 30 days unless they specify otherwise.

## Tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `beta_city_entries` | Every city Go/chip attempt (raw + resolved, launch vs not) |
| `beta_activity_notify` | Email dedupe ledger (one/browser/city/UTC day) |
| `beta_feedback` | In-app feedback submissions |
| `beta_consents` | Consent acceptances |
| `beta_invitees` | Outbound email roster |

## City demand (non-launch cities)

```sql
SELECT raw_city,
       COUNT(*) AS attempts,
       COUNT(DISTINCT distinct_id) AS users
FROM beta_city_entries
WHERE NOT is_launch_city
  AND created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY raw_city
ORDER BY attempts DESC
LIMIT 25;
```

## Daily Go vs rejected (launch gate)

```sql
SELECT DATE(created_at AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') AS day,
       COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE is_launch_city) AS launch,
       COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE NOT is_launch_city) AS rejected,
       COUNT(*) AS total
FROM beta_city_entries
WHERE source = 'go'
  AND created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1 DESC;
```

## Go vs chip volume

```sql
SELECT source,
       COUNT(*) AS entries,
       COUNT(DISTINCT distinct_id) AS users,
       COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE is_launch_city) AS launch,
       COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE NOT is_launch_city) AS not_launch
FROM beta_city_entries
WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY source
ORDER BY entries DESC;
```

## Launch city breakdown

```sql
SELECT COALESCE(resolved_city, raw_city) AS city,
       COUNT(*) AS entries,
       COUNT(DISTINCT distinct_id) AS users
FROM beta_city_entries
WHERE is_launch_city
  AND created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY entries DESC;
```

## Recent city entries (last 20)

```sql
SELECT created_at, raw_city, resolved_city, is_launch_city, source, distinct_id
FROM beta_city_entries
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

## Activity emails sent today (UTC)

```sql
SELECT raw_city, resolved_city, is_launch_city, source, distinct_id, notified_at
FROM beta_activity_notify
WHERE activity_day = (NOW() AT TIME ZONE 'UTC')::date
ORDER BY notified_at DESC;
```

## Feedback summary (30 days)

```sql
SELECT issue_type,
       COUNT(*) AS n,
       ROUND(AVG(sentiment)::numeric, 1) AS avg_sentiment
FROM beta_feedback
WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days'
GROUP BY issue_type
ORDER BY n DESC;
```

## Funnel headcount (distinct browsers, 30 days)

```sql
SELECT
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT distinct_id) FROM beta_city_entries
   WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days') AS city_entries,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT distinct_id) FROM beta_feedback
   WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days') AS feedback,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM beta_consents) AS consents_total;
```
